events.632: Islam entered Yemen during the Rashidun Caliphate.
events.819: Banu Ziyad becomes independent from the Abbasid state.
events.1021: Banu Ma'an becomes independent from the Ziadian state.
events.1513: Aden unsuccessfully attacked by the Portuguese under Albuquerque.
events.1538: Aden taken by Ottoman forces of Hadim Suleiman Pasha.
events.1869: Suez Canal opens in Egypt, affecting Aden as a port.
events.1937: City becomes capital of the British Colony of Aden.
events.1963: Aden becomes part of the Federation of South Arabia.
events.1967: Aden becomes capital of People's Republic of South Yemen; British forces depart.
events.1975: Suez Canal reopens, affecting port of Aden.
events.1990: City becomes part of the newly formed Republic of Yemen.
events.-700: The emergence of the Awsan Kingdom in Aden.
events.-110: Himyarites overthrow the Kingdom of Saba and Qataban and take control of Aden.
events.1420s: Chinese explorer Zheng He visits Aden.
